          <div id="main-content">
            <h2>Malca Pass Library</h2>
            <div id="pos_content" class="cms_position">
              <div id="mod_12" class="cms_module">
<p style="text-align: justify;">The <strong>Malca Pass Library</strong> collection includes biographies, books on art, Jewish religious practice, holy days, history, kosher cooking, music, philosophy, and fiction by Jewish authors. The library also holds many excellent films and documentaries.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><br /><br />Especially exciting is the <strong>Sadie Lieff Judaic Software Collection</strong>. This wonderful resource features computer programs for learning Hebrew, chanting the Torah, gaining insight on Jewish history, and more. <strong>The Margarethe Benice and Esther Freedman Music Collection</strong> is unique in Ottawa and includes hundreds of compact discs featuring <em>Chazzanut,</em> Klezmer, Ladino, and popular Israeli music.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">The <strong>Malca Pass Library</strong> also sponsors <strong>book reviews</strong> and events throughout the year.&nbsp; Best of all, <strong>everyone in the community is welcome</strong> to make use of our wonderful collection, or come to our programs.&nbsp;</p>
<h2 class="h2" style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="/uploads/a/1a%20malca%20pl.pdf" target="_self">Click here for the list </a></strong></h2>
<h2 class="h2" style="text-align: center;"><strong><a href="/uploads/a/1a%20malca%20pl.pdf" target="_self">of the 2015- 2016 Book Reviews.</a></strong></h2>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><br /><br /><strong>In 2011</strong>, the <strong>Malca Pass Library celebrated 50 years</strong> <strong>of continuous operation and</strong> <strong>received renewal of its advanced accreditation by the American Association of Jewish Libraries in recognition of its excellent collection and its professional operation, a rare honour for synagogue libraries.</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><br /><br /><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>NEW WINTER Hours of Operation</strong></span><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong><br /></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="line-height: 1.4;">Thursday&nbsp; 11:00 am - &nbsp;2:00 pm</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>&nbsp;<br /></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">The <strong>Malca Pass Library</strong> is closed on all Jewish and Statutory holidays.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Click on the following link to access the catalogue - <strong><a href="https://gfl.follettdestiny.ca/common/welcome.jsp?site=201&amp;context=ca01_6019057_est" target="_self">CATALOGUE SEARCH</a></strong><a href="%20https://gfl.follettdestiny.ca/common/welcome.jsp?site=201&amp;context=ca01_6019057_es" target="_self">.</a></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>For additional information, please contact Estelle Melzer at 613.722.0721 or <a href="mailto:estelle.melzer@gmail.com">estelle.melzer@gmail.com </a><br /></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><br /><br style="text-align: justify;" />&#65279;</p>

</div>
